{"type": "article", "id": 47255, "title": "肯德基日本推出炸鸡入浴剂，7-Eleven 台湾做的拍手墙有点魔性 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-11-15T03:31:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 179, "name": "星球大战"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}, {"id": 45531, "name": "7- Eleven"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 81, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171115104716n53ozZ0y78YSURO6.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #323231; -webkit-text-stroke: #323231; background-color: #f0f3fb} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23984.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>摩托罗拉又找陈坤拍广告了</b></a>，这次念了一首诗《致少数人》，不过陈坤只在广告开头结尾各念了一句话。陈坤在今年十月成为摩托罗拉品牌代言人，这是他为摩托罗拉拍摄的第二支广告，比起之前一个“少数人”系列，摩托罗拉终于直白地开始介绍产品，而不是拍了一段让人摸不着头脑的风景大片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=t05011nir3t&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-16-42665.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>肯德基和日本杂货店 VILLAGE VANGUARD 推出炸鸡味道的入浴剂</b></a>，外型、气味和包装完全模仿了肯德基炸鸡。据说躺进这样的泡泡浴里，感觉就像是在油锅里炸鸡一样。此前肯德基也在美国市场推出过炸鸡味防晒，在香港地区推出过指甲油。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171115112251rc2bSi149WqJogNA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711151123146hEZ0gt78mb5fFDI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171115112344J7kYojnTR9OiUz8t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} span.s1 {font: 14.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23939.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>ADK TAIWAN 为台湾 7-11 做了一面“爱的鼓励墙”</b></a>，看起来有点魔性。只要在捐款箱中投下零钱或纸钞，便能启动红外线感应机制，12 双高仿小手便会立刻为你的善行拍拍手。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=j0504dz9ims&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #323231; -webkit-text-stroke: #323231; background-color: #f0f3fb} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23985.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>菜鸟裹裹拍了支双十一收包裹神曲《亲，你的快乐发货啦》</b></a>，找的是菜鸟驿站的站长们出镜，连唱带演还挺有意思。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=g0503et1nxq&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #323231; -webkit-text-stroke: #323231; background-color: #f0f3fb} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #323231; -webkit-text-stroke: #323231; background-color: #f0f3fb; min-height: 21.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23962.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为了推广 8.0 新版本，百度网盘以韦小宝升职记为主题做了个 H5,</b></a> 分别根据三个新功能拍了小故事。手机用户<a href=\"http://pan.geekeer.cn/index.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">可点击这里体验</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171115105929Stmk9IhjfArnR12W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728571\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; min-height: 19.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #011480; min-height: 14.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23595.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Google 翻译在朋友圈投放了广告，欧阳靖露了个脸</b></a>。Google 翻译在今年三月向中国用户开放，但此事与 Google 重返中国无关。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=t0561lyxh6y&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/creativity/playstation-just-made-one-of-the-best-star-wars-ads-in-a-while-thanks-to-strong-storytelling/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>PlayStation 的《星战前线2》预告片拍得很带感</b></a>：讲述了一对中二少年和少女从小站星战的不同阵营相爱相杀，从小打到大的故事，效果堪称大片，女主的邪魅笑容也值得反复观看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=z05041akg0g&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\">题图来源：KFC</p>"}